        <title>CIRCUIT FUNCTION</title>
        <para>The ECM (Electronic Control Module) provides an output for a remote tachometer with a 0 - 12 volt digital
            signal that indicates engine speed. The frequency sent by the ECM is 1/5th of the actual engine RPM.
        </para>
